{"tid":2175990,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"公鹿火箭雷霆棄賽聲援Jacob Blake","createTime":"2020-08-26T22:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T00:23:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1d51b5bad06093b8ba682dc9aea47e49829048","tid":2175990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T22:37:54.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】公鹿、火箭、雷霆球員因為黑人男子Jacob Blake遭白人警察槍擊一事，決定杯葛周三NBA賽事。<br />\n<br />\nESPN著名籃球記者Adrian Wojnarowski於Twitter爆料，公鹿原定在周三NBA季後賽東岸第1圈第5戰鬥魔術，大軍原本已經到達球場的更衣室，但最終為了向Jacob Blake被槍擊一事表態，決定不出賽。<br />\n<br />\n據知在公鹿球員作出決定時，一眾NBA高層都在更衣室外等候，但未有入內。至於魔術大軍早就到場上熱身，只是最終未能出戰。除了公鹿之外，火箭、雷霆都杯葛賽事<br />\n<br />\n美國種族歧視問題最近再度升溫，繼早前黑人男子George Floyd遭白人警員以膝頭壓頸致死後，另一黑人男子Jacob Blake最近在威斯康辛州，被白人警察執法時近距離從後開7槍，據律師表示，Jacob暫時從腰部以下癱瘓，可能再也無法走路。"},{"pid":"30e234b6fb3466b6819c2714561665cf94a37502","tid":2175990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T22:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgYDCAgVoAIrki0?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEgYDCAgVoAIrki0%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=e100fe6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d2bfb9b72448fdec3f7c17436d7a49900928dc","tid":2175990,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T22:46:16.000Z","msg":"班玩具佬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d4c0f5bd6471abe35de07f2e0c8653a2a7fb12","tid":2175990,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25d2bfb9b72448fdec3f7c17436d7a49900928dc","tid":2175990,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T22:46:16.000Z","msg":"班玩具佬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T22:48:09.000Z","msg":"Ching狼狗"},{"pid":"bfe1f6d83925f79b1585f1e04fd0be7b61aa7d8a","tid":2175990,"ui